HART vs. BOARD OF SUPERVISORS (Genesee), No. 14800, 105 M., 209.

(Certiorari to Genesee.)

To compel respondents to audit relator’s account, under 3 How. Stat., Sec. 2155, for building a fish chute in his dam.

The circuit judge granted the writ. Affirmed April 30, 1895, with costs.
